#  ██▄▪▐███ ██▌▐█▌▐█▌▐█▌ ▄▐███▌▐█▄▪▐█  ═╩╝╚═╝ ╩ ╚  ╩╩═╝╚═╝╚═╝
#  ·▀▀▀▀ ▀▀  █▪▀▀▀▀▀▀.▀▀▀ ·▀▀▀  ▀▀▀▀   https://dot.bmilcs.com
#                 DOT LOG DEBUGGING UTILITY [./dotlog]

log="${BMLOGS:-~/.config/bmilcs}/dotfile_$USER.log"
touch "$log"

# env var override
#if [[ $BMDEBUG == "1" ]]; then
  # . ~/bin/sys/bmlogger "$log"
  # sh $BM/bin/bin/sys/bmlogger "$log"

   dotc() {
       echo > "$log"
       _a dotlog
       _i cleared
   }

   dotls() {
     sed -i -e 's/\/home\/bmilcs/~/g' "$log"
     cat "$log"
   }

   dotlog() {
     echo "[$(date "+%m.%d.%G | %r")] $*" >> "$log"
   }
